{"tid":1803163,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"五毛新策略: 黃店? 但佢貴喎 難食喎 唔靚喎","createTime":"2019-12-30T04:09:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-30T04:24:50.000Z","uid":144001,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"39b162edcc30d237ff954c57d3231be49dc454a4","tid":1803163,"uid":144001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T04:09:05.000Z","msg":"屌曬你地老母啦 黃店係唔需要講太多品質同價錢<br />\n因為品質好易改 價錢有得傾 但<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">良心跌左就唔知去左邊</span></span><br />\n<br />\n黃色經濟圈就係先問良心 再講其他<br />\n五毛<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"855c6d4d2f4687e913f9d4b6408a41dcb6a3bc46","tid":1803163,"uid":101906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T04:09:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e84def10983af039119917e2db33f5a12d68f2ae","tid":1803163,"uid":68777,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T04:10:17.000Z","msg":"如果覺得龍門唔好食，轉食光榮o唔ok<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5722c96ca4e89b4b11c3a86acc58ad18393cb26a","tid":1803163,"uid":49178,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T04:10:25.000Z","msg":"我買嘅係服務😉😉可能無咁好食 但至少食得舒服"},{"pid":"20fe8edb3c96e323805ec22958cec55e9f62d3d2","tid":1803163,"uid":279090,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T04:11:06.000Z","msg":"其實可以即時向店家反映<br />\n怕羞嘅寫喺張單度都得"},{"pid":"f60feeac31281692065c8f2e88d8b997c6d50156","tid":1803163,"uid":144001,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e84def10983af039119917e2db33f5a12d68f2ae","tid":1803163,"uid":68777,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T04:10:17.000Z","msg":"如果覺得龍門唔好食，轉食光榮o唔ok<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T04:13:12.000Z","msg":"轉食其他黃店 但唔好discourage 其他人去任何黃店"},{"pid":"d35939d1adc18d81e11f32629a89d20e24308432","tid":1803163,"uid":134744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T04:13:52.000Z","msg":"有意見可以友善同鋪頭反映<br />\n最緊要係良心同骨氣"},{"pid":"28fe13b472a16bfbeda5c79b9a4d2c9e68791002","tid":1803163,"uid":77393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T04:17:48.000Z","msg":"道理好簡單 幫襯黃店 罷食藍店<br />\n<br />\n黃店唔係開善堂 品質係要有基本保證先確保繼續有錢賺 係基本商業世界定律嚟 難食/性價比唔高就自然少咗幫襯 唔需要刻意放大佢係咪黃店"},{"pid":"9d466077c0db44507b30edc491bfe7b154712164","tid":1803163,"uid":46411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T04:24:50.000Z","msg":"罷食藍店我認同<br />\n間黃店難食咪食另一間黃店囉<br />\n唔通食屎咩<br />\n有部分黃店真係難食到嘔 唔開名啦廢事話我打手五毛"}]}